OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDefoe 'appalled' by fan's  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBradley Lowery taunt       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Jermain Defoe has said he was "appalled
OL,6, and saddened" by a Sheffield Wednesday 
OL,7, supporter who mocked the death of      
OL,8, Sunderland mascot Bradley Lowery.      
OL,10,FDale Houghton, 31, taunted opposition  
OL,11,Ffans with an image of the six-year-old 
OL,12,Fwhen the two teams played on Friday.   
OL,14,FHe admitted a public order offence     
OL,15,Fbefore Sheffield magistrates on Monday.
OL,17,FEx-Sunderland striker Defoe formed a   
OL,18,Fclose bond with Bradley, who he called 
OL,19,Fhis "best mate", before his death from 
OL,20,Fcancer in 2017.                        
